Package inb370.asgn1

Interface Summary
IHiringGame Abstract representation of the Hiring Problem also known as the Secretary Problem.
 

Class Summary
Applicant Represents an applicant in the Hiring Game.
Game This class is used to start the game.
GamePanel The actual GUI components used to run the game and also stores the current game state.
HiringFrame This class is the outermost container for the game's GUI components.
 

Exception Summary
HiringException This class represents any exceptions generated by the Hiring Game.
